<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-1385] nodetool cfstats does not update after adding new cfs through API</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1385</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Start a 3 node cluster. Add a new Keyspace with API. Then add more CFs to that Keyspace. ndoetool cfstats will only show you the CF which was originally part of KsDef creation and not the CfDefs that were added later.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;CentOS 5.2&lt;br/&gt;
Trunc&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12471485">CASSANDRA-1385</key>
            <summary>nodetool cfstats does not update after adding new cfs through API</summary>
